document.full_text: nasdaq omx group's  failed bid for long-time rival nyse euronext  was a "brief interlude" for management and a disappointment, and now the exchange is moving on, its chief executive said on thursday.
document.title: nasdaq's failed nyse bid a "brief interlude": ceo
